{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "被追逐者", "storyInfo": "倫蒂尼姆碎片大廈內，特雷西斯注意到了羅德島的靠近。與此同時，阿米婭、推進之王與博士正帶隊靠近倫蒂尼姆。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "theater", "attributes": {"mode": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "倫蒂尼姆 奧克特里格區", "x": 290.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 30.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "碎片大廈內部", "x": 290.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.02, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "theater", "attributes": {"mode": "false"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i01", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的工程已近尾聲。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我聽到了風暴的聲音，他們也聽到了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們正在向我訴說，他們喜歡這個聲音。他們迫不及待地想要變成風暴的一部分，肆意地在空中吼叫，去吞吃我們眼前這座可恨的城市。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那正好。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十天之後，飛空艇就會竣工。到時候，他們就能去往倫蒂尼姆的上空，成為這場風暴的引航員。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會和他們一起去。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這符合我們的計畫。既然我需要守著碎片大廈，那你就是指揮我們的空中力量的最佳人選。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，特雷西斯，我不是這個意思。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和他們，我們只能一起去。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你們動身之前，你還需要繼續履行你的職責。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王庭需要你，我們的戰士也需要他們最信任的君主。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你本就比我更擅長建設。自從你開始出席王庭會議，我們的施工速度加快了百分之十。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會忘了我應該做什麼。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，我注意到，你撤掉了那些......守衛。赦罪師沒少抱怨你吧？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撤掉你周圍的守衛是軍事委員會的決定。我們需要更多崗哨，來應對最關鍵時期的危機。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要的話，我也可以去戰場。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你留在這裡。這座塔......還有飛空艇，這才是我們計畫的核心。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等這兩項工程徹底完成，卡茲戴爾將擁有對抗所有國家的力量。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對抗所有國家嗎......", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我從來都知道你的野心，但每次聽見，都難免有些不可置信。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是總擔心著他們會不容許我們重新崛起嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快就沒這個必要了。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——如果我們連風暴的走向都能掌握，又有誰還會去憂慮飄到頭頂的陰雲？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去我們薩卡茲任由敵人們追逐。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一次次地在廢墟中站起來，一次次地重建家園，又一次次地看著我們的家被他們挑起的戰爭撕扯成碎片。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i01", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$rebel_intro", "key": "$rebel_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲......薩卡茲。我們是無根之人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是為什麼？只因為他們占去了最好的土地，不允許我們紮根。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩百年前那場戰爭中，我們傾盡全力，才將外敵打退——但是我們依然沒能保住卡茲戴爾。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，我們花了多少時間，才勉強將流落各地的殘部重新召集？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們又花了多少時間——", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才能在維多利亞和烏薩斯的眼皮子底下，將一些他們看不上的碎片運至他們同樣看不上的荒地，將卡茲戴爾再度建起？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩百年？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我們花去了整整兩百年。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那下一次呢？假如我們的卡茲戴爾再一次毀於戰火，我們又需要多少時間才能將它重建？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五百年——還是更久？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敵人們就快得逞，正因為我們已經習慣了流浪。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次又一次的毀滅，或許永遠無法泯滅薩卡茲的精魂，卻在事實上打散了我們。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的卡茲戴爾只是擁擠的居所，不是家。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更多的薩卡茲遊蕩在外面的大地上，眼裡只有明天的麵包，卻沒有更遠的夢想。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連王庭......卡茲戴爾空有十王庭的傳說，大半王帳都已空置。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以你才想要這場戰爭。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是我想要，而是薩卡茲需要。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，戰火將自我們腳下燃起。維多利亞、烏薩斯、萊塔尼亞......沒有一座城市、一片土地能夠倖免。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在接下來的一百年內，敵人們不會再有餘力將目光投向卡茲戴爾。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不僅如此。等我們擁有了引領風暴的能力——他們將反過來畏懼薩卡茲的注目，就如他們畏懼著風暴降臨。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風暴......正聚於我們所處的這處塔頂。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會看見身處風暴核心的我們。任何薩卡茲的敵人都會竭盡全力撲上來阻止我們。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就讓他們來吧。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你不怕第一道雷落下的時候，你也會烈焰焚身嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你建起巴別塔的時候，你也知道所有反對者都會將刀劍指向你——你那時可曾怕過？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你用生命建起的高塔已經坍塌，就像上一座卡茲戴爾一樣。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而此時此刻，我們站在這裡——一座新的塔，一個新的機會。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看今天的倫蒂尼姆吧。你剛剛主持了諸王的會議。難道你沒有發現？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連我們之間那場無用的戰爭開始之前，薩卡茲也從未如此接近團結。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "x": 490.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "xTo": 490.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「我正準備回到城外的軍營裡，特蕾西婭殿下。」", "x": 500.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "x": 100.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "xTo": 100.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「我明白，食腐者之王。我們這次會議會儘量簡短些。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「你總是這麼來去匆匆啊，食腐者。你是不想與我們相聚嗎？」", "x": 100.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "x": 490.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "xTo": 490.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「我可沒你那麼清閒，血魔。倫蒂尼姆之外屯著十萬大軍，\\n我和我的將士們沒有一刻能夠鬆懈。」", "x": 500.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "「那不如交換吧，我正好厭煩了城內那些貴族的喋喋不休。」", "x": 100.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 1180.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "「特雷西斯，你那個高盧的小朋友也一樣愚蠢而且聒噪。」", "x": 100.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 1180.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "「我可不敢保證什麼時候我會失去耐心。」", "x": 100.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 1180.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.6, "yScaleFrom": 1.6}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.6, "yScaleFrom": 1.6, "xScaleTo": 1.7, "yScaleTo": 1.7, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「他的腦袋還得在脖子上待一段時間。別讓城內的維多利亞軍隊給我們增加麻煩。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「那好吧。不過，你不覺得還有人沒派上用場嗎？」", "x": 100.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "x": 390.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.6, "yScaleTo": 1.6, "xTo": 390.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「你說我嗎，血魔？我接下來可有大事要辦，對吧，殿下們？」", "x": 500.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i12", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 50.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「當然。想要控制倫蒂尼姆，離不開你們每一位的努力。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「你派出去的信使都有消息了嗎，赦罪師？」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「在曼弗雷德的不懈勸說下，巫妖已在趕來倫蒂尼姆的路上。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 100.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「僅剩的溫迪戈仍在烏薩斯北境對抗精怪。他們心中已沒有王庭。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 100.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「獨眼巨人送回了一封信，一如既往，她描述了一個悲慘的場景——倫蒂尼姆被大火撕扯成了三塊，碎片大廈倒在數百道閃電之下，而攝政王......是的，她還預言了攝政王殿下的結局。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 100.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「說出來。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「她說她看到了你孤獨地死在聖王會西部大堂地下的王座上。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 100.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「回信給她，感謝她的關心。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「繼續搜尋石翼魔的消息。但凡能尋到任何遺落的血脈，立刻向他們發出邀請。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「委員會將和眾王庭一起，確保這場戰爭的勝利。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 600.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i01", "fadetime": 1.2}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果薩卡茲還能有獲得新生的機會，那麼眼下就是那個唯一的機會。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......又會有很多人死去。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多......維多利亞人，也有很多薩卡茲。人們的鮮血將會徹底改變這座灰色的城市，人們的哀嚎甚至將蓋過雷聲。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一場戰爭。一場我們與他們之間的戰爭，持續了近萬年，從未結束。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，戰爭......這從來就是我們薩卡茲存續下去的方式。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有任何異議的話，說出來。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像過去無數次那樣，指出我計畫中的風險。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有異議。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有......嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你能聽到我腦海裡的聲音，你就會知道，他們不會讓我有第二種選擇。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若這場戰爭真的能讓卡茲戴爾擺脫毀滅的循環......倘若這場風暴真的能澆滅薩卡茲的恨火，令無數亡靈重歸自由......", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我會與你一起，確保我們的理想能夠實現。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣也好。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一件事——", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島的人，他們已經在路上了。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g3_minearea_abandoned", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "6:50 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距倫蒂尼姆五百二十七公里，廢棄礦場作業平台"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 凱爾希醫生，停泊程式將在一小時四十八分鐘之後啟動。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好。在這之前，確保接舷區能正常使用。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白，我們會加緊排障。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 華法琳，危重病人是否都安置妥當了？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 放心，還差最後三個明天就要手術的，移動病床馬上就能整理出來......", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 別催我好不好？你板著臉往這裡一站，我們的醫療幹員都還要忍不住多瞄你幾眼。", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#10$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......情況緊急。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好啦，我知道，不開玩笑。", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 自從進入維多利亞，我們哪一天不是過得像打仗一樣。要不是那麼多幹員都被你提前調走......", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#8$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅德島需要照常運轉。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 華法琳，在第一次決議會上，我們就已經達成共識。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我沒意見啊。四年前你讓Mon3tr把我綁上這條船......", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我是說邀請我加入羅德島的時候，我們可是說好了，我是作為醫生來和你一起研究礦石病的。", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 什麼“跟隨著新任魔王一起打回卡茲戴爾”，從來就不在我的合約條款裡，就算把卡茲戴爾替換成倫蒂尼姆也一樣。", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 對我們許多幹員來說，都是如此。我也無意強制任何一位幹員投入和他們長期目標無關的任務中。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 更何況，哪怕我們有其他不得不採取的行動，也不能置遍佈各地的感染者於不顧。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉，要不是還有這些工作，去倫蒂尼姆的精英幹員還能多幾位。", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_171_bldsk_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也不知道阿米婭他們怎麼樣了......", "name": "華法琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_171_bldsk_1#4$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等他們抵達倫蒂尼姆附近，我們會收到消息。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wild_m", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 偵察小組，彙報兩側情況！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......收到。確認沒有威脅。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可露希爾，前方可通行，工程隊跟上！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  收到！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " Dr.{@nickname}，你還走得動嗎？要不要讓我的無人機載你一程？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "還好，接著走吧。;......;無人機什麼時候能有這項功能？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line252", "option2": "line252", "option3": "line253"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line256"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line256"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我想想啊......這主意似乎還真不錯。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士，我們再堅持一下，等步行穿過這片危險地帶，我們就能登上載具，稍做休整。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 到時候我們也該給凱爾希醫生發個信了......她一定非常擔心我們。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不知道本艦那邊順不順利。;她也該給我們發個信。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line264", "option2": "line267"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line275"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這就是凱爾希醫生必須留下的理由......只有安置好了羅德島，她才能與我們會合。這是我們共同的責任。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line275"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 安全起見，我們在靠近倫蒂尼姆的這段路途上不能使用發報機。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿米婭", "content": " 任何信號都可能會被附近的公爵軍隊截獲。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿米婭", "end": "true", "content": " 不，或許更糟......博士，我們不能給特雷西斯這麼早就發現我們的機會。", "joined": " 任何信號都可能會被附近的公爵軍隊截獲。 不，或許更糟......博士，我們不能給特雷西斯這麼早就發現我們的機會。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士，請放心交給我吧。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿米婭", "content": "從羅德島計畫駛入維多利亞開始，你與凱爾希醫生一直在忙著確保行駛路線的安全，"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿米婭", "end": "true", "content": "我們說好了，接下來這段路由我負責更多一點。", "joined": "從羅德島計畫駛入維多利亞開始，你與凱爾希醫生一直在忙著確保行駛路線的安全，我們說好了，接下來這段路由我負責更多一點。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我希望你也能喘口氣......哪怕只是精神上的也好。", "name